{"word":"Book","slug":"book","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Book</b> Genealogies kept in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=5&verse=1'>Gen 5:1</a><br/> Law of Moses written in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=5&verse=23'>Num 5:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=17&verse=18'>Deu 17:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=31&verse=9'>Deu 31:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=31&verse=24'>Deu 31:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=31&verse=26'>Deu 31:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=22&verse=8'>2Ki 22:8</a><br/> Topography of Palestine, recorded in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=18&verse=9'>Jos 18:9</a><br/> Chronicles of the times kept in:<br/> - By Jasher<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=10&verse=13'>Jos 10:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=1&verse=18'>2Sa 1:18</a> <br/> - By Samuel, Nathan, and Gad<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=10&verse=25'>1Sa 10:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=29&verse=29'>1Ch 29:29</a> <br/> - By Iddo<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=12&verse=15'>2Ch 12:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=13&verse=22'>2Ch 13:22</a> <br/> - By Isaiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=26&verse=22'>2Ch 26:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=32&verse=32'>2Ch 32:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=8&verse=1'>Isa 8:1</a> <br/> Of the kings of Judah and Israel:<br/> - Of the kings of Judah and Israel:<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=27&verse=24'>1Ch 27:24</a> <br/> - Of Solomon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordo